---

<Layout title="关于 - AIInfraGuide" description="关于 AIInfraGuide 作者草帽路飞">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background effects -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-500/[0.07] dark:bg-blue-500/[0.10] rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-40 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-violet-500/[0.05] dark:bg-violet-500/[0.09] rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <article class="py-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- Hero / identity -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-24 h-24 mb-6 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 ring-1 ring-gray-200/60 dark:ring-white/10">
          <img
            src={getPath('/images/caomaolufei.png')}
            alt="草帽路飞头像"
            width="96"
            height="96"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          草帽路飞
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          互联网大厂 AI Infra 在职 · AIInfraGuide 作者
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
          {expertise.map((tag) => (
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[13px] font-medium bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/[0.06] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 border border-gray-200/60 dark:border-white/[0.06]">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- About section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          <span class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#007aff]"></span>
          关于我
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-[15px] md:text-base leading-[2.4] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <p>
            你好！我是 <strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">草帽路飞</strong>，目前在互联网大厂从事 AI Infra 方向的研发工作，拥有多年相关工作经验，主攻<strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">模型训练、推理和算子优化</strong>方向。
          </p>
          <p>
            我也是开源项目 <a href="https://github.com/caomaolufei/AIInfraGuide" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-[#007aff] dark:text-[#0a84ff] hover:underline">AIInfraGuide</a> 的作者——这是一套「从 0 入门 AI Infra 全栈」的学习教程，希望帮助更多人系统性地构建从底层 CUDA 编程到分布式训练、推理优化的完整知识体系。
          </p>
          <p>
            我硕士研究方向为传统高性能计算（HPC），主要从事面向 CPU 与 GPU 异构平台的数值模式优化工作，在算子级优化与系统级性能调优方面具备较为扎实的积累。硕士期间拥有 3 段 AI Infra 相关实习，毕业后通过校招加入某大厂从事 AI Infra 研发至今。
          </p>
          <p>
            做这个项目的初衷，是把工作中零散积累的知识重新梳理成体系，也希望和更多对 AI Infra 感兴趣的朋友一起交流成长。后续我会结合一线工程实践，持续输出学习笔记与系统化教程～
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          <span class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#007aff]"></span>
          联系方式
        </h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
          {contacts.map((c) => {
            const inner = (
              <>
                <span class={`inline-flex items-center justify-center w-11 h-11 rounded-xl ${c.bg} ${c.accent} mb-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:scale-110`}>
                  <svg class="w-[22px] h-[22px]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="none">
                    <path d={c.icon} />
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <span class="block text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-1">{c.label}</span>
                <span class="block text-[15px] font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white break-all leading-snug">{c.value}</span>
                {c.href && (
                  <span class="absolute top-5 right-5 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#007aff] dark:group-hover:text-[#0a84ff] transition-colors duration-200">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                )}
              </>
            );
            return c.href ? (
              <a
                href={c.href}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group relative block p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/[0.06] bg-white dark:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-[#007aff]/40 dark:hover:border-[#0a84ff]/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/5 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer"
              >
                {inner}
              </a>
            ) : (
              <div class="group relative block p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/[0.06] bg-white dark:bg-white/[0.03]">
                {inner}
              </div>
            );
          })}
        </div>

        <!-- WeChat group QR -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/[0.06] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-white/[0.04] dark:to-white/[0.01]">
          <img
            src="https://caomaolufei.github.io/AIInfraGuide/images/wx_qun.png"
            alt="AIInfraGuide 微信交流群二维码"
            width="240"
            height="240"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-40 h-40 shrink-0 object-contain rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white"
          />
          <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">加入AIInfraGuide交流群</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              扫码加入 AIInfraGuide 微信交流群，与更多 AI Infra 同好一起讨论训练、推理与算子优化的实战经验。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Personal WeChat QR -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/[0.06] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-white/[0.04] dark:to-white/[0.01]">
          <img
            src={getPath('/images/caomaolufei_vx.jpeg')}
            alt="草帽路飞个人微信二维码"
            width="240"
            height="240"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-40 h-40 shrink-0 object-contain rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white"
          />
          <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">草帽路飞个人微信</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              扫码添加我的个人微信，一起交流 AI Infra 学习与实战经验，也欢迎技术合作与探讨。另外需要【求职咨询/学习规划/求职陪跑】等服务的可以加我。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-white/[0.06] flex justify-end">
        <a
          href={getPath('/about/roadmap')}
          class="group flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-[#007aff] dark:hover:text-[#0a84ff] transition-colors duration-200 cursor-pointer"
        >
          教程更新计划
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
